{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He would give-- he would take the ammunition out of the rifle and he'd give the last guy to carry his rifle, and one guy would carry his belt, and the other one was that, until we got about maybe half a kilometer before the kitchen, and he'd put his garb back on.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This went on for a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, consequently, he sort of became lax on his guard, and we became very alert.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what was happening, when we got back to the camp at night, the elders would say, while you guys are peeling the potatoes, and you're doing all the thing, why don't you cut some potatoes in half, and carrots in half, so we can get better food and more nourishment?",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we went back to the kitchen, and we started a system.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we would cut the potatoes, and this and that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got away with it for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we got a little greedy, because hunger is a very, very, very, very hurting thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we started to bring food back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would just put strings around our waist, and on the bottom of our cuffs of the-- of these burlap uniforms we had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would load those up with carrots, and cabbages, and potatoes, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since this was in the fall in Bavaria, so it gets dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the old man, he knew what we were doing, but he, at that point, was very kind of lax.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we kept bringing this stuff in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we gave it to the-- you know, we gave it our elders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because we ate as much as we wanted to in those kitchens.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
